cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.SY

This paper discusses the need for secure communication and management of IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a framework architecture for device management, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper discusses the need for key management services to support access control and networked resources, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
